{"words":[{"word":"te","count":4},{"word":"nobles","count":2},{"word":"aye","count":2},{"word":"href","count":2},{"word":"capitoline","count":2},{"word":"hill","count":2},{"word":"city","count":2},{"word":"looking","count":2},{"word":"seen","count":2},{"word":"around","count":2},{"word":"ano","count":2},{"word":"teams","count":1},{"word":"year's","count":1},{"word":"finals","count":1},{"word":"backed","count":1},{"word":"local","count":1},{"word":"'s","count":1},{"word":"holding","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"agon","count":1},{"word":"happens","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"four","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"septimont's","count":1},{"word":"talkin'","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"champion","count":1},{"word":"games","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"ferries","count":1},{"word":"heading","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"anyone","count":1},{"word":"ragunnesi","count":1},{"word":"troupe","count":1},{"word":"fools","count":1},{"word":"montelli","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"open","count":1},{"word":"ways","count":1},{"word":"thinking","count":1},{"word":"faith","count":1},{"word":"wearing","count":1},{"word":"order's","count":1},{"word":"emblem","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"drawn","count":1},{"word":"eyes","count":1},{"word":"gladly","count":1},{"word":"ever","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"ancestors","count":1},{"word":"set","count":1},{"word":"foot","count":1},{"word":"land","count":1},{"word":"septimontians","count":1},{"word":"fought","count":1},{"word":"harsh","count":1},{"word":"elements","count":1},{"word":"savage","count":1},{"word":"tacet","count":1},{"word":"discords","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"brave","count":1},{"word":"souls","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"reverberations","count":1},{"word":"settlin'","count":1},{"word":"stone","count":1},{"word":"stands","count":1},{"word":"lioness","count":1},{"word":"glory","count":1},{"word":"arsinosa","count":1},{"word":"born","count":1},{"word":"battle's","count":1},{"word":"roar","count":1},{"word":"fierce","count":1},{"word":"bellows","count":1},{"word":"pride","count":1},{"word":"order","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"askin'","count":1},{"word":"inns","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"best","count":1},{"word":"fights","count":1},{"word":"follow","count":1},{"word":"path","count":1},{"word":"arena","count":1},{"word":"ticket","count":1},{"word":"booth's","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Most of the teams in this year's finals aren't even backed by local nobles.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Aye.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Aye. <te href=850167>Capitoline Hill</te>'s holding the <te href=850149>Great Agon</te> now in the city. Happens every four years. All of Septimont's talkin' about who'll be the next champion. You here for the games too?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Who's it you're looking for? This here is the first stop for ferries heading to Capitoline Hill. Maybe we've seen them before.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"...Can't say I've seen anyone like that around.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Most Ragunnesi we see here are from the Troupe of Fools or the Montelli nobles. They're a bit more open to our ways of thinking about faith.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"If she's wearing the Order's emblem, though, she'll have drawn some eyes.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Gladly! See, ever since our ancestors set foot on this land, we Septimontians have fought the harsh elements and the savage Tacet Discords.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Many brave souls came before us, their Reverberations settlin' in the stone that now stands as <ano=Lioness of Glory>Arsinosa</ano>. She was born from the battle's roar and the fierce bellows of pride.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"As for that Order girl you're looking for, you might try askin' in the inns around the city...","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Ah, right, we best be off. If you want to see the fights, follow this path to the arena. The ticket booth's just up ahead.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125}]}